\c 28
\s UEfrayimi uyaxwayiswa
\p
\v 1 Maye kumqhele wokuzigqaja\x + 28.3,5.\x* wezidakwa zakoEfrayimi, obuhle benkazimulo yazo\x + 28.4,5. 4.2.\x* buliluba elibunayo, eliphezu kwekhanda lezihotsha ezivundileyo\x + 28.4,5. 4.2.\x* zalabo abatshaywe liwayini.
\v 2 Khangela, iNkosi ilaye olamandla loqinileyo\x + 2 Kho. 17.5,6.\x*, ozaphosela emhlabeni ngesandla, njengezulu lesiphepho elilesiqhotho\x + 30.30. 32.19. Isam. 11.19.\x*, isiphepho esichithayo\x + Hlab. 91.6.\x*\x + 29.6. 28.15. Hez. 13.11.\x*, njengempophoma yamanzi alamandla\x + 17.12.\x* akhukhulayo\x + 29.6. 28.15. Hez. 13.11.\x*\x + Amos 5.7.\x*.
\v 3 Umqhele wokuziqgaja\x + 28.3,5.\x* wezidakwa zakoEfrayimi uzanyathelelwa phansi ngezinyawo.
\v 4 Lobuhle benkazimulo yakhe\x + 28.4,5. 4.2.\x*, obuphezu kwekhanda lesihotsha esivunde kakhulu\x + 28.4,5. 4.2.\x*, buzakuba liluba elibunayo, njengesithelo esivuthwe masinyane kungakafiki ihlobo\x + Hos. 9.10. Mika 7.1. Jer. 24.2.\x*; okuthi osibonileyo asibone, sisesesandleni sakhe asiginye.
\p
\v 5 Ngalolosuku\x + 2.11.\x* iN\nd kosi\nd* yamabandla izakuba ngumqhele wenkazimulo\x + 28.1.\x*, lesidlodlo sobuhle\x + 28.4,5. 4.2.\x* kunsali yabantu bayo,
\v 6 lomoya wesahlulelo kulowo ohlalela isahlulelo, lamandla kulabo ababuyisela impi esangweni\x + 22.7. Hlu. 5.8.\x*.
\v 7 Lalaba baduhile ngenxa yewayini\x + Zaga 20.1. Hos. 4.11.\x*, langenxa yokunathwayo okulamandla baphambukile\x + 19.14.\x*; umpristi lomprofethi baduhile ngenxa yokunathwayo okulamandla\x + 56.10,12. Levi 10.9.\x*, baginywe liwayini, baphambukile ngenxa yokunathwayo okulamandla; bayaduha embonweni, bakhubeke kusahlulelo\x + Jobe 31.28.\x*.
\v 8 Ngoba wonke amatafula agcwele amahlanzo \add lo\add*kungcola, kakulandawo \add engangcolanga\add*.
\p
\v 9 Izafundisa bani ulwazi\x + Jer. 6.10.\x*, njalo izakwenza bani aqedisise umbiko? Abalunyuliweyo echagweni\x + Mat. 11.25. 18.3.\x*, abakhunyuliweyo emabeleni.
\v 10 Ngoba umthetho phezu komthetho\x + 28.13,17.18.2. Hlab. 19.4.\x*, umthetho phezu komthetho; umzila phezu komzila, umzila phezu komzila; lapha okuncinyane, laphayana okuncinyane.
\v 11 Ngoba ngendebe eziklolodayo langolunye ulimi\x + 30.4. 1 Kor. 14.21.\x*\x + 32.4. Hlab. 81.5.\x* izakhuluma kulababantu,
\v 12 eyathi kubo: Lokhu yikuphumula\x + 30.15. Mat. 11.28,29.\x*, phumuzani abadiniweyo\x + Hlab. 63.1.\x*; lalokhu yikuvuselela; kodwa kabathandanga ukuzwa\x + 30.4. 1 Kor. 14.21.\x*.
\v 13 Kodwa ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* lizakuba kibo ngumthetho phezu komthetho, umthetho phezu komthetho\x + 29.10.\x*; umzila phezu komzila, umzila phezu komzila\x + 28.10.\x*; lapha okuncinyane, laphayana okuncinyane; ukuze bahambe, bawe nyovane\x + 8.15.\x*, bephuke\x + 8.15.\x*, bathiywe\x + 8.15.\x*, bathunjwe\x + 8.15.\x*.
\p
\v 14 Ngakho zwanini ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd*, bantu abaklolodayo\x + 28.22. 29.20.\x*, elibusa lababantu abaseJerusalema.
\v 15 Ngoba lithe: Sivumelane isivumelwano lokufa\x + 28.18.\x*, njalo senze isivumelwano lesihogo\x + 28.18.\x*; lapho isiswepu esiphuphumayo sisedlula\x + 28.2,17,18. Jobe 5.21.\x*, kasiyikufika kithi; ngoba senze amanga aba yisiphephelo sethu\x + 28.17. Roma 1.25.\x*, sacatsha ngaphansi kwenkohliso\x + 28.17. Roma 1.25.\x*.
\v 16 Ngakho itsho njalo iNkosi uJehova: Khangela, ngibeka eZiyoni\x + 1 Pet. 2.6.\x* ilitshe\x + 8.14. Gen. 49.24. Hlab. 118.22. Jer. 51.26.\x* lesisekelo, ilitshe elihloliweyo\x + Luka 23.35.\x*, ilitshe lengonsi eliligugu\x + 8.14. Gen. 49.24. Hlab. 118.22. Jer. 51.26.\x*, isisekelo esisekelweyo\x + 1 Kor. 3.11. Hlab. 87.1.\x*; okholwayo kayikuphangisa\x + 1 Pet. 2.6.\x*\x + Roma 10.11. Hlab. 25.2.\x*.
\v 17 Isahlulelo laso ngizasibeka entanjeni\x + 28.10.\x*\x + 2 Kho. 21.13.\x*, lokulunga entanjeni yokuqondisa\x + 2 Kho. 21.13.\x*; lesiqhotho\x + Jobe 38.23.\x* sizakhukhula isiphephelo samanga\x + 28.17. Roma 1.25.\x*; lamanzi agabhele\x + 28.2,17,18. Jobe 5.21.\x* indawo yokucatsha\x + 28.17. Roma 1.25.\x*.
\v 18 Lesivumelwano senu\x + 28.18.\x* lokufa sizaphela, lokuvumelana kwenu lesihogo kakuyikuma\x + 28.18.\x*; lapho isiswepu esikhukhulayo sisedlula\x + 28.2,17,18. Jobe 5.21.\x*, khona lizanyathelelwa phansi yikho.
\v 19 Kusukela esikhathini sokwedlula kwaso, sizalithatha; ngoba ukusa ngokusa sizakwedlula, emini lebusuku\x + 50.4.\x*; njalo kuzakuba ngokwesabisayo\x + Dute. 28.25.\x* kuphela ukuqedisisa umbiko\x + 28.9. 53.1.\x*.
\v 20 Ngoba umbheda mfitshane kakhulu ukuthi \add umuntu\add* azelule \add kuwo\add*, lengubo yincinyane kakhulu ukuthi \add umuntu\add* azigoqele \add ngayo\x + 25.7.\x*\add*.
\v 21 Ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* izavuka njengentab\add eni\add* yePerazimi\x + 2 Sam. 5.20. 1 Lan. 14.11.\x*, ithukuthele njengesigodi\add ni\x + Josh. 10.10,12. 2 Sam. 5.25. 1 Lan. 14.16.\x*\add* seGibeyoni\x + Josh. 9.3.\x*, ukuze yenze umsebenzi wayo, umsebenzi wayo ongejwayelekanga, yenze isenzo sayo, isenzo sayo esingejwayelekanga.
\v 22 Ngakho-ke lingahleki usulu\x + 28.22. 29.20.\x*, hlezi izibopho zenu ziqiniswe; ngoba ngizwile eNkosini uJehova wamabandla \add ngo\add*kuqedwa okuqunywe phezu komhlaba wonke\x + 10.23.\x*.
\s Inhlakanipho kaNkulunkulu
\p
\v 23 Bekani indlebe, lizwe ilizwi lami; lalelani lizwe inkulumo yami.
\v 24 Umlimi ulimela ukuhlanyela lonke usuku yini? Uyavula abhuqe umhlabathi wakhe yini\x + Jobe 39.10.\x*?
\v 25 Kakunjalo yini, esewuhlelembile ubuso bawo, ukuthi aphose \w amafitshizi\w**, ahlakaze \w ikhumini\w**, afake phezu \add kwakho\add* ingqoloyi enhle kakhulu, \w lebhali\w** emisiweyo, \w lespelite\w** emngceleni wakho?
\v 26 Ngoba uNkulunkulu wakhe uyamazisa ngendlela\x + Hlab. 112.5. Hlab. 94.10.\x*, amfundise.
\v 27 Ngoba amafitshizi kawabhulwa ngobhulo\x + 21.10. Jobe 41.30.\x*, levili lenqola kaliphendulwa phezu kwekhumini\x + Zaga 20.26.\x*; kodwa amafitshizi atshaywa ngoswazi\x + 27.12.\x*, lekhumini ngentonga.
\v 28 \add Amabele\add* esinkwa ayachotshozwa; ngoba kayikuhlala ewabhula kokuphela, loba ewachoboza \add nge\add*vili lenqola yakhe, njalo kawachobozi ngamabhiza akhe.
\v 29 Lalokhu kuvela eN\nd kosi\nd*ni yamabandla; iyamangalisa ekwelulekeni\x + Hlab. 92.5. Jer. 32.19.\x*, yinkulu ekusebenzeni\x + Jobe 5.12.\x*.
